channel.title: Bank booth
channel.description: Hi guys, I need some help with a small problem I'm having with my bank booth. When a player clicks on the bank to "use" the bank doesn't show up however it does show up for "quick-use" I will leave a Gif under this to show you what I mean. Can anyone help? The source is 317 Delta. [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/GSN8zCq.gif[/img]

item.title: Bank booth
item.dc:creator: @ik0u2 ik0u2
item.description:
@ik0u2 wrote:

Jmood:

make sure you have the bank booth added to your first click packet, all you will most likely need to do is copy and paste from the second click packet.

Thank you, it was this.
